dct_title_s: Meiji kaisei Tōkyō zenzu; Sagano, Hikotarō.; Tōkyō zenzu;Tōkyō kubetsu hitori annai
dct_description_sm: Keikikaku zō. Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the upper right. Relief shown by hachures. Includes lists of town names, and train destinations and fares. Ill. points of interest in border. Inset: Yokohama shigaizu. 1 map: col.; 53 x 73 cm., folded in covers 19 x 10 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
